    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 guidance. Output comparison achieves gradation 3, exceeding the required gradation 2. The UQ campaign (documented in validation results VR-01 and VR-02) confirmed that the 95th-percentile RH uncertainty band of ±0.07 does not affect the accept/reject decision under the RH < 1 criterion. The credibility assessment is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
